-- MOVES-ANZ names Mary MacLeod international and institutional banking CFO
-- 
-- Wed Jul 16, 2014 06:02AM EDT
-- None



July 16 (Reuters) - The Australia and New Zealand Banking Group Ltd (ANZ) <ANZ.AX> said it appointed Mary MacLeod chief financial officer for international and institutional banking.

She will report to Shayne Elliott, the company's CFO, and Andrew Geczy, chief executive for international and institutional banking, ANZ said. MacLeod will be responsible for managing the financial performance and regulatory reporting for international and institutional banking across ANZ's 33 markets, the company said.